Class Message

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.triceo.splitlog.Message

  • public final class Message

      • equals

        public boolean equals(Object obj)
        Two Messages are equal if and only if they have the same getUniqueId(). This effectively means no two distinct ones will ever be equal.
        Overrides:

      • getUniqueId

        public long getUniqueId()
        Unique ID of the message, that can be used to compare messages in the order of their arrival into this tool.
        Returns:
        ID of the message, guaranteed to be unique for every message, and increasing from message to message.
